This paper deals with the problem of distributed aggregation in wireless networks, which is a key issue in the field of computer networks. The paper focuses on the challenges posed by highly dynamic environments, which are typical of wireless networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Other possible categories include cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MA (Multiagent Systems).
